        <text>
          <![CDATA[ <p><strong>Taiwan Defense Act of 2021</strong></p> <p>This bill establishes that it shall be U.S. policy to maintain the ability of the U.S. Armed Forces to defeat attempts by China to invade and seize control of Taiwan before U.S. forces can respond effectively.</p>]]>
        </text>
